@{
    Layout = "_AuthLayout";  // بدون هيدر وفوتر
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy - Eventa";
}

@section Styles {
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f8fafc;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .privacy-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 32px;
            padding: 4rem 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            color: transparent;
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
        }

        .last-updated {
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
            color: #1e293b;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

            h2::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 0;
                left: 0;
                width: 70px;
                height: 4px;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
                border-radius: 2px;
            }

        p, li {
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }

            ul li {
                margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
                position: relative;
            }

                ul li::marker {
                    color: var(--primary-color);
                }

        strong {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 5rem;
            padding-top: 2.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
        }

        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .privacy-container {
                padding: 3rem 2rem;
                border-radius: 24px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2.4rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
}

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: December 01, 2025</p>

    <p>At <strong>Eventa</strong>, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email, password (encrypted), profile photo</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Processed securely via third-party providers (we do not store card details)</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Events viewed, tickets purchased, device info, IP address</li>
        <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Support messages, feedback</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
        <li>To process ticket purchases and send confirmations</li>
        <li>To send important updates about your bookings</li>
        <li>To personalize your experience</li>
        <li>To prevent fraud and enhance security</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We share your information only when necessary:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>With event organizers (name & email for ticket delivery)</li>
        <li>With payment processors</li>
        <li>When required by law</li>
        <li>With trusted service providers (hosting, analytics)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, update, or delete your personal data</li>
        <li>Opt out of marketing emails</li>
        <li>Request data export</li>
        <li>Delete your account</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your data. However, no method is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2>6. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to improve your experience. You can control cookies via browser settings.</p>

    <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Our site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.</p>

    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Eventa is not intended for children under 16. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

    <h2>9. Changes to Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy. We will notify you of material changes via email or platform notice.</p>

    <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
        Questions about privacy? Email us at
        <a href="mailto:privacy@eventa.com">privacy@eventa.com</a>
    </p>

    <div class="footer-note">
        &copy; 2025 Eventa. Protecting your privacy, always.
    </div>
</div>